text:
You're doing quite well!
Keep up the good work with the next characters!

It's probably better
to check them yourself!

...
That's true! I'll go check them now!

Oh, as expected of Natsuha.
You're fast, and you seem totally at ease.

Hehe, of course.
I train for moments like these.
So, how do the characters look...?
Oh! They're looking good, aren't they?

Producer!
Let's have Kaho take a picture of this!

Yeah, that's a good idea――
but you don't have to pull me so hard...

What are you saying! They might get blown away by the wind!
Come on, let's go quickly!
